             was indicted for <rs id="t17840915-6-off28" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840915-6-off28" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840915-6-off28" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               feloniously assaulting 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840915-6-victim152" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Tucker
                        <interp inst="t17840915-6-victim152" type="surname" value="Tucker"></interp>
